00:41:04.037 --> 00:41:05.870
So I think it is important
that we dismantle

00:41:05.870 --> 00:41:08.720
that myth for girls,
and we really teach them

00:41:08.720 --> 00:41:11.300
what healthy
relationships look like,

00:41:11.300 --> 00:41:13.970
and how to navigate
disagreements,

00:41:13.970 --> 00:41:17.200
and how to make
people feel included.

00:41:17.200 --> 00:41:19.870
I have a six-year-old
