leadership behavior.

00:41:33.740 --> 00:41:36.290
When you have influence, and
when you reach out to somebody,

00:41:36.290 --> 00:41:37.697
and when you're
inclusive, what's

00:41:37.697 --> 00:41:39.530
that change that you're
